_header: This world wondereth of all thing
_description: A carol of the Incarnation — five three-line stanzas (aaa) + burden (bb): ‘VEni redemptor gencium / veni redemptor gencium’

BodArcSelB26.First Lines:
This worle wondreþ of al thyngehowe a maide conceyued a
                    kynge…
BodArcSelB26.Last Lines: …vs to thy ioye for to brynge
